:Constant_Probability0 rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                                :DeterministicParameter ,
                                :Parameter ;
                       :hasDataItemType :DI_Probability ;
                       :hasExpectedValue "0.0"^^xsd:double .


###  https://w3id.org/ontologies-ULL/OSDi#Constant_Probability1
:Constant_Probability1 rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                                :DeterministicParameter ,
                                :Parameter ;
                       :hasDataItemType :DI_Probability ;
                       :hasExpectedValue "1.0"^^xsd:double .


